show.title: Twisted Fates
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/wYpLXy
show.description: Middle-class family man Finch navigates the delicate balance between duty and desire when his orderly life is suddenly upended. Devoted to creating a stable future for his beloved wife Mira and their young son, Finch's unwavering dedication is put to the ultimate test as forbidden emotions emerge. When lines blur between family loyalty and unexpected passion, the ripple effects of his choices threaten everything he's built. A mesmerizing exploration of human connection, temptation, and the profound consequences of following one's heart, no matter the cost.
